HEADWORD: Tronage
<hw>Tron"age</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From <er>Trone</er>
a steelyard.]</ety> <def>A toll or duty paid for weighing wool; also,
the act of weighing wool.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Nares.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

